  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nAfter upgrading to 5.1.50, Truffle does not work when configured to use a Websocket provider. \r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nI have a project that was working correctly in 5.1.49. It is configured to use a Websocket provider. After upgrading to 5.1.50, it does not work. After changing the configuration to not use a Websocket provider, it works.\r\n\r\nThe failure occurs immediately when running `truffle test`.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nI expected the tests to run normally.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n(I've redacted my local path information with `...`)\r\n```> Something went wrong while attempting to connect to the network. Check your network configuration.\r\nProviderError: \r\n    at .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/provider/wrapper.js:75:1\r\n    at  .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/provider/wrapper.js:107:1\r\n    at Object.callback ( .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/packages/provider/wrapper.js:112:1)\r\n    at  .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/node_modules/web3/node_modules/web3-providers-ws/src/index.js:133:1\r\n    at Array.forEach (<anonymous>)\r\n    at WebsocketProvider._onMessage  (.../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/node_modules/web3/node_modules/web3-providers-ws/src/index.js:118:1)\r\n    at W3CWebSocket._dispatchEvent [as dispatchEvent] ( .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/node_modules/yaeti/lib/EventTarget.js:115:1)\r\n    at W3CWebSocket.onMessage ( .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/node_modules/websocket/lib/W3CWebSocket.js:234:1)\r\n    at WebSocketConnection.<anonymous> ( .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/node_modules/websocket/lib/W3CWebSocket.js:205:1)\r\n    at WebSocketConnection.emit (events.js:315:20)\r\n    at WebSocketConnection.processFrame ( .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/node_modules/websocket/lib/WebSocketConnection.js:554:1)\r\n    at  .../node_modules/truffle/build/webpack:/node_modules/websocket/lib/WebSocketConnection.js:323:34\r\n    at processTicksAndRejections (internal/process/task_queues.js:79:11)\r\nTruffle v5.1.50 (core: 5.1.50)\r\nNode v12.18.4\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: MacOS 10.15.7\r\n* Ethereum client: Truffle / Ganache\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): Truffle v5.1.50 (core: 5.1.50)\r\n* node version (`node --version`): Node v12.18.4\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): 6.14.6\r\n",
